<span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span> Dion Chang is one of South Africa’s most respected trend analysts and founder of Flux Trends, which takes the unique view of “trends as business strategy”. Flux Trends specialises in identifying unexpected business opportunities within shifting trends, specifically the impact of disruptive technologies – across all industries – ensuring that global trends have relevance when translated for African and South African businesses. Dion is passionate about assisting companies to embrace change and embedding a culture of innovation into corporate operating systems. As a result, he is used as a management consultant for businesses facing change and struggling to adapt to new world order. Brought to you by Nedbank Private Wealth.